{"tid":1534164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民權法通過前...黑警不斷濫捕","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T13:18:22.000Z","uid":193220,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"79e23e71ff1a1345bba425785c471de6c00c57cd","tid":1534164,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:19:43.000Z","msg":"證明咗我地做得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一通過咗民權法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警準備仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地會變成林鄭condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港有超過200萬市民甚至仲更加多<br />\n<br />\n黑警你拉得幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人一日都打不死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民權法通過前，黑警不斷濫捕<br />\n<br />\n睇黎黑警真係好驚民權法通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警你地不斷濫捕都冇用<br />\n只會反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國國會都好大機會通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位香港人唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9.8 I Love 美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10.1 送大禮俾中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警/高官你們...... 多行不義必自斃<br />\n小心你地有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲巴打絲打唔好再圍狗屋<br />\n只會送頭，唔值得<br />\n撚狗都有好多方法<br />\n或者留氣力機場或者10.1國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！！！缺一不可！！！<br />\n<br />\nWe are Hongkonger ^_^<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家PUSH"},{"pid":"defc4c6b0b86c23d0eae6f85a6210b28b5a4b170","tid":1534164,"uid":193220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:20:26.000Z","msg":"大家加強文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1ecffe421e2be1c90bf81e8e4a3521f50e9003","tid":1534164,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:22:27.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span>