gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民權法通過前，黑警不斷濫捕<br />\n<br />\n睇黎黑警真係好驚民權法通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警你地不斷濫捕都冇用<br />\n只會反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國國會都好大機會通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位香港人唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9.8 I Love 美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10.1 送大禮俾中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警/高官你們...... 多行不義必自斃<br />\n小心你地有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲巴打絲打唔好再圍狗屋<br />\n只會送頭，唔值得<br />\n撚狗都有好多方法<br />\n或者留氣力機場或者10.1國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！！！缺一不可！！！<br />\n<br />\nWe are Hongkonger ^_^<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家PUSH"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">太子現場FA指：<br />\n-黑警要FA交出身分證明同FA證先比救，故意延誤急救<br />\n-傷者有氣促，FA建議解手扣抒緩，黑警唔比；建議除衫，黑警又話係證物唔比，最後bargain一輪只比剪開一半，又故意將人道急救置於執法之下<br />\n-傷者頸椎腫 有血 應有骨折傷勢 氣促，昏迷至離開上白車<br />\n-黑警圍住走，唔比任何人跟車，或者問去邊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n殺人犯名單<br />\n1669 鍾國恩 警長<br />\n48958 李彼得 高級警員<br />\n54538 張文麟 高級警員<br />\n58248 梁智顯 高級警員"},{"pid":"84e08bef13966f3a1cd641c52326235fc0ae10f4","tid":1534164,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201